verbose_text: Moreover, in SFN treated MDA-MB-231 cells, mRNA levels of SIN3A (transcriptional co-repressor and histone deacetylase complex subunit Sin3A), SAP18 (Sin3A associated protein 18 and histone deacetylase complex subunit SAP18) and SAP30 (Sin3A associated protein 30 and histone deacetylase complex subunit SAP30) were downregulated.
